Rating: 4
This recipe is delicious. The only thing I did differently was add the dried mango and coconut at the same time I added the sugar and orange zest. My dried mango was quite hard and leathery and I wanted the liquid and heat of the rice and milk to soften it up. Also, after reading other reviews, I only added two tablespoons of sugar and the next time I make this recipe I will only add one (or even a little less).

